milestones.description: Otieno has broken the record for most ducks (6) in ODIs for KENYA, going past Martin Suji's 5
Martin Suji and Ababu's 21-run partnership is KENYA's highest for the 10th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 15 between Hitesh Modi and Joseph Angara
This is the lowest match aggregate (382) involving teams India & Kenya in ODIs
Odumbe has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (32) for KENYA, going past Otieno

stories.title: India beat Kenya by 58 runs
stories.summary:
Nairobi - India, after a very difficult start, recovered well to defeat
Kenya by 58 runs in match four of the LG Cup in Kenya
